                  <img class="u-photo" src="/assets/images/no-profile-photo.png" data-src="https://pkcdn.xyz/commentpara.de/ef200c8b639d79d1cfbc0abf0e25f42dcbc585b4398003dd90f5a56c9d56e3bf.svg" width="48">
