              </div>
                                <!-- TODO: should this be e-summary if I've truncated it or if it came from the summary? -->
          <div class="e-content p-name comment-content">Most of the micropub implementations are islands; people built their own client and their own server, and those two speak with each other. Real interoperability (clients speaking with different servers) has not been achieved yet.</div>
